Located in Historic Downtown Mount Dora, Florida, Maggie's is a family owned wine and beer cellar and eclectic boutique. Operated by Terry and Stephanie, along with Jerome the resident Sommelier, Adrianne the resident beer monger and Ben who is our favorite product sampler, all brothers and sister. Maggie's opened for business in October 2003 with the goal of creating a fun, casual atmosphere in which our guests could enjoy themselves while expanding their knowledge of wines and craft beers, enjoy the company of great people and even make new friends. When at Maggie's everyone is family! Maggie's offers everyone some very special activities each month. On the 1st and 3rd Saturdays each month we host our Wine Tasting events, open to the public and our club members, featuring more than 20 new and different wines at each tasting. Casually stroll the streets of Mount Dora to the different tasting venues. Enjoy light appetizers along the way and take in the live music at Maggie's. The 2nd Saturday each month brings our Beer Tasting event. Enjoy sampling the 20 or more different craft beers presented each month. Share the fun with other beer enthusiasts, have a piece of pizza and enjoy our live music. Every day is a great day to stop by and relax with your favorite wine or beer.
